sources.title: The Agency (2001) Deadline
sources.description:
When a newspaper article reveals that a high ranking KGB man worked for the U.S. during the cold war. The man fearing what will happen if he's exposed alerts the C.I.A. Pierce who was his handler must try to find a way to protect the man especially since a KGB man who likes to weed out traitors, is close to finding out who the "one" is.

Director: Mikael Salomon
Writer: Michael Frost Beckner

Main Cast:
Ronny Cox – Director Alex Pierce III
Gil Bellows – Matt Callan
Rocky Carroll – Carl Reese
Gloria Reuben – Lisa Fabrizzi
Paige Turco – Terri Lowell
David Clennon – Joshua Nankin
Will Patton – Jackson Haisley

Genres: TV Series, Crime, Drama, Action, Mystery & Thriller
Release Date: December 20, 2001

Availability varies by region
